Answer from John Son: Hello ABHAY, To change the Invoice email use this code in the function.php file of the active theme and replace the test@gmail.com with your email // Add custom email to Invoice add_filter( 'pdf_template_admin_email', 'change_pdf_template_admin_email' ); Example: add_filter( 'pdf_template_admin_email', 'change_pdf_template_admin_email' );
function change_pdf_template_admin_email() {
return 'test@gmail.com';
} For the HSN Category, I am forwarding these details to our technical team Thank you Regards, John

